definition: TOEFL/Test of English as a Foreign Language
(old) thanks to your lucky influence (polite reply to health inquiries)
prop/support (for weight)/rest (e.g. arm rest)/thanks to/to hold in one's hand/to support in one's palm/to give/to base/to commit/to set/torr (unit of pressure)

sentences.english: Why didn't you take TOEFL, IELTS or SAT tests?
sentences.chinese: 你为什么没有考雅思或是托福，赛达考试？

sentences.english: What does the ETS have changes in TOFEL for?
sentences.chinese: 您觉得ETS在托福上作的修改是出于什么目的？

sentences.english: The minimum requirement for TOEFL we have is 79, Internet-based.
sentences.chinese: 我们对托福的最低要求是网考79分。

sentences.english: Tell us your early experience of training TOFEL test.
sentences.chinese: 能说说看您早期的一些从事托福考试培训的经历吗？

sentences.english: I got a high score on TOEFL.
The IELTS also has a speaking section, unlike the paper version of the TOEFL.
sentences.chinese: 雅思还有一个口语部分，与托福的全部笔试截然不同。

sentences.english: I am preparing for the TOFEL test.
sentences.chinese: 我在准备参加托福考试。

sentences.english: She was going to reenter for TOEFL.
sentences.chinese: 她将重新报名参加托福考试。

sentences.english: Please fill in the highest TOEFL score obtained and provide us with photocopies of the results slips.
sentences.chinese: 请填写获取的最高托福测验分数并提交成绩单副本。

sentences.english: Yes. I’ve passed the TOEFL test.
sentences.chinese: 是的，我已经考过了托福。

sentences.english: He wanted to study abroad, but he failed to pass the TOFEL test.
sentences.chinese: 他想出国念书，但他没通过托福考试。

sentences.english: As from today, NEEA starts to accept online registration.
sentences.chinese: 自即日起，考试中心开始接受新托福考试网上报名。

sentences.english: Yes, you hve to tke the Toefl test.
I took the TOEFL and received a score of 620 points.
sentences.chinese: 我考过托福，我的分数是620。

sentences.english: Something you will only get after you fail to pass TOEFL.
sentences.chinese: 那些考托福失败后才懂得的事。

sentences.english: But some say the increase is still not big enough.
sentences.chinese: 但有人则认为此次托福网考扩容的幅度还不够大。
